case.title: Wingman needed for 33 SWF - 33 (Upper East Side)
case.text: Social awkward female in search of a good time out on the town. Bar hopping drinking, meeting men, and having fun. I don't get out to often and I have forgotten what fun is, help me remember. 33 SWF wanting to become more social active but needs guidance and lots of help. In return I will become a good friend. I have Monday night off
